During Spring 2024, I took ICS212 where I learned C and C++. Being quite uncomfortable with C++, I decided to code something simple in order to enhance my knowledge in it. It contained classes, recursion, vector, and others. You can play with two players or with a CPU using a minimax algorithm. 
